{"tid":1264611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"都係做港豬算啦，起碼自己人生仲可以活得有意義","createTime":"2019-06-28T18:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T10:58:01.000Z","uid":235588,"like":22,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"58d86278fd83de637b5a070ecacff0d86d733f99","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:39:22.000Z","msg":"利申返先，我有去69,616,然後發夢去埋探狗狗，但係身累心累都不及對香港死左條心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明白香港人打左咁耐仗，5想咁就打退堂鼓，所以下下發夢係到諗佔領、包圍XX<br />\n<br />\n然後所謂升級都係<br />\nXX由政總&gt;警總&gt;律政司<br />\n<br />\n但係就從來無從佔領、包圍升級到更高嘅層面，例如發夢武裝革命<br />\n<br />\n咁既然香港人抗爭心理上無準備好升級層面，下下就升級XX，但下場都係散水or驅散，咁有乜7用？如果大家最後有一定包袱所以去唔到最盡，咁點解唔坦白咁接受個現實？另一方面，中共係一個不斷狀大嘅怪獸，我地可能進步咗一倍，但人地係十倍，咁我地仲要抗爭、自取滅亡？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為一個步向永恆嘅煉獄付出時間、心血，卻一無所有。我想引用天琦係地厚天高講過嘅感受：有陣時唔想擔旗上身，而係想做返自己鐘意嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n我預左比人吊，不過想講，天真地擁抱希望係荒謬過接受絕望。"},{"pid":"060cc5431a880e3e0c67f3f4f733993367517958","tid":1264611,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:41:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98b04b72070d21a4350327c251e84a58f5fdd83f","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"幫你地諗埋，個終極升級行動：包圍中聯辦，直搗中共在港基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376a47672fc3228143ee5114284f670b33ab7293","tid":1264611,"uid":48579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:43:18.000Z","msg":"諗係容易 做係好難 呢場仗唔係一局定勝負 <br />\n要慢慢打 希望巴打回心轉意 <br />\n再一齊發夢上前線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac39a3a7e8739ad23c038f0d411ed617416606cc","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:44:27.000Z","msg":"香港運動特色：和平地升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a87deb0a3f89122664029a30ce941371b538cd","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:47:37.000Z","msg":"希望連登仔係講道理講務實嘅。壯士斷臂好過戰死一切先投降啦"},{"pid":"294375048388f8eda901693d3c475283d0921e97","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:54:10.000Z","msg":"大家有眼睇，616二百萬人有幾多個仲follow up成個運動？ 612佔領係最多人嘅，然後到621，然後近兩三次發夢佔領，個人數愈嚟愈少。代表咩？ 我尊重出嚟抗爭嘅每一位犧牲個人利益，但去到呢刻，我寧願做個位contrarian，希望出去嘅每一位過返自己嘅人生。<br />\n<br />\n香港玩完係事實，中共係不斷壯大、不可擊倒嘅怪怪，亦都係事實。認清現實，把握光陰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442d69348275f32d3ff306efe42aa580d05ca5dc","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:58:07.000Z","msg":"你5找上絕望，絕望會找上你"},{"pid":"852c5fc1e607ac658d0e8acd7800c6279d500a4b","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:59:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"57dc7d526070cd3f4a738b15c01f97fcb025df80","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:00:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a01aa7ee1d015fe5378ec20a5ff82cf95c6f01f8","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:02:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7fff6f6438760223c2f8d80d2176f7e43a0bbe7d","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:02:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"70a9cce772a1de95f5dc0987c637c36be3702dc3","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T19:06:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db194d5403533532407fe8edec7b5128db84c517","tid":1264611,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTi